==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: hatchet man
<hw>hatchet man</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A person hired to
murder or physically attack another; a hit man.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A person who deliberately tries to ruin the
reputation of another, often unscrupulously, by slander or other
malicious communication, often with a political motive, and sometimes
for pay.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hatchettite</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Hatchettine</ent>⟦br⟧
